httping
------------------------------------------

Ping-like program for http-requests

Show how long it takes to connect to a hostname or remote
url; send a request and retrieve the reply (only the headers).

Runtime requirements:
  libgcc1
  libopenssl100

Build requirements:
  quilt
  openssl-devel

