Build instructions:
  unpack httping-2.4+20151029+gitb1521a6-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
    unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  ./httping*.sh all

This will create:
  httping-2.4+20151029+gitb1521a6-1.tar.xz
  httping-2.4+20151029+gitb1521a6-1-src.tar.xz

